1. Iteration / Transformation

forEach() â†’ Loops through each element (does not return a new array).

map() â†’ Transforms each element and returns a new array.

filter() â†’ Returns a new array containing only elements that match a condition.

reduce() â†’ Reduces the array to a single value (sum, average, object, etc.).

some() â†’ Returns true if at least one element passes the condition.

every() â†’ Returns true if all elements pass the condition.

find() â†’ Returns the first element that matches the condition.

findIndex() â†’ Returns the index of the first element that matches the condition.

ðŸ”¹ Adding / Removing Elements

